{"tid":730074,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"忽然球迷入邊，邊班最核凸？","createTime":"2018-07-05T06:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T12:53:57.000Z","uid":32051,"like":74,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"520f8cce3ddaa1c2cc91d86ca59c40f624e3a3a5","tid":730074,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:01:47.000Z","msg":"我就點睇都係日本隊既忽然球迷最核凸<br />\n日本人民族意識係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但成班人不斷幫佢打飛機就好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾kingjer條打手衰到講自己2:0果時瞓著俾人反cup無睇到好唔開心，都可以一大班港女留言身同感受咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係未見過有球迷2:0時，俾對家撳住黎砌都可以瞓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即係日本球員清左個更衣室係好<br />\n但日本當地都搞到新宿同池袋成地垃圾<br />\n全部人都盲撚黎既 選擇性無視<br />\n不斷講日本點好點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都未計佢地講到比利時贏波罪大惡極咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b2051677fc55936d07397003eb074158ca5d2d","tid":730074,"uid":11381,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:02:50.000Z","msg":"冰島"},{"pid":"c8db22e3ccc8681053ff6e37b079c6601bbe7c73","tid":730074,"uid":45189,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:04:04.000Z","msg":"泡菜"},{"pid":"4646053186eb17ab0442ce98bc9dd8509d373a4c","tid":730074,"uid":103914,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:04:41.000Z","msg":"英格撚"},{"pid":"75d44e664d488a43883cecb52e784955211e8259","tid":730074,"uid":1977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:05:04.000Z","msg":"冰島最肉酸"},{"pid":"a89235dafbb75ee5681a2666792fa18b720788f7","tid":730074,"uid":192678,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T06:06:07.000Z","msg":"最聯"},{"pid":"aab302508da8fd72a92bcff4fb30a098d8a7cdb1","tid":730074,"uid":32051,"like":6,"dislike":20,"score":-14,"quote":{"p